name: Listened to Week #1 Recap Show: vs Bethune-Cookman

Orange Bowl BoysWeek #1 Recap Show: vs Bethune-CookmanShow NotesThe Mario Cristobal Era got underway with a 70-13 win against Bethune-Cookman at the Rock on Saturday. The Canes new look offense put up 605 yards and the defense did its job (with little issues here and there). The Boys give their thoughts on the team’s performance.
